text: Obradoiro Club de Amigos do Baloncesto is a Galician basketball team. It was founded in 1970. The team currently plays in league ACB. == Major trophies == * Prince's Cup of Basketball: 1 ** 2010/11 * Copa Galicia de Baloncesto (Galician League): 9 ** 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2019 == References == Category:1970 establishments in Europe Category:1970s establishments in Spain Category:Basketball teams in Spain Category:Santiago de Compostela
